		============================
		Lustre Monitoring Tools (v2)
		============================


Client software --
	lwatch
	lstat
	ltop

Prerequisites:

	ant (needed by charva package only)
	jdk1.4 or higher

============
Simple Build
============

To build everything from scratch:

	./configure
	make

(Run './configure --help' to see how to specify the paths for ant, java, javac.)

==============
Partial Builds
==============

To build just the LMT java applications:

	./configure (just once)
	make charva (just once)
	make all

To build an LMT application jar file:

	make jar

To build a complete LMT application jar file plus
all external (3rd party) jar files:
	
	make fulljar


